articles.author: Eric Bradner
articles.title: Trump’s 2024 victory revealed voter shifts that could reshape America’s political landscape - CNN
articles.description: President-elect Donald Trump won across the map — improving on Republican margins nearly everywhere and delivering on his promises to win over more non-White voters on his way to defeating Vice President Kamala Harris.
